    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54B32 powerhouse, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, both meticulously serviced to ensure a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM limit. The chassis is structurally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, a critical enhancement for long-term rigidity. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. Every component, from the Sachs dampers to the bushings and cross-drilled rotors, remains in peak operational state, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative care. This is a museum-quality, turn-key machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
