      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. The exterior retains its original factory luster, free from any stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings, and has been recently treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the upholstery shows no creasing or wear, the dashboard remains crack-free, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist technologies, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, featuring a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has been strictly garage-kept, never seen rain or snow, and drives with the precision of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking perfection without compromise.",
